name: Global X Crude Oil ETF
longDescription: Each Commodity ETF is designed to provide investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to the performance of its specified Underlying Index. None of the Commodity ETFs invest in the physical spot commodity market.
fulldescription: Each Commodity ETF is designed to provide investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to the performance of its specified Underlying Index. None of the Commodity ETFs invest in the physical spot commodity market. Any U.S. dollar gains or losses as a result of the Commodity ETFs investments will be hedged back to the Canadian dollar to the best of their ability HUC seeks investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to the performance of the Solactive Light Sweet Crude Oil Winter MD Rolling Futures Index ER.
